assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醒個下個陣失落 根本形容唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4719a1e829168d1ef3141b6e6668cff12e7c25f2","tid":235131,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔信你大熱天時 30幾度都沖勁熱水涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係芬蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b83841f757de7509418d254ad9b448cf7de727","tid":235131,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:56:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩又沖完個熱水涼 唉 飲返罐啤酒又再發過夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f985965cae9e25f84c54b521d27a5339a9112b35","tid":235131,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒不可耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毒得太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dab46ae453deec77f2b6ca60e2017aabe2cbf4","tid":235131,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:58:06.000Z","msg":"活係回憶中 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好需要一個人叫醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc01496af971b0438192f101b1c83dc9180f9754","tid":235131,"uid":114432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:01:02.000Z","msg":"毒係邊??<br />\n樓主有俾人攬過先知俾人攬住係咩感覺<br />\n但好多人連攬都未俾人攬過<br />\n<br />\n樓主已經好幸福架喇"},{"pid":"dd6f1022b1a2834eb69cab11f3e9a2489ca8a5b9","tid":235131,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:02:14.000Z","msg":"叫雞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb308f70d5f16aa8bc4270ec5c9a0d6759b5ef4","tid":235131,"uid":109486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:02:15.000